Class DataSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.awt.Component
      • java.awt.Container

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible, javax.swing.ScrollPaneConstants

    public class DataSet
extends javax.swing.JScrollPane
    The class that keeps track of the data in each DataSet in the GraphArea. It contains the columns with the x,y, and error/uncertainty value as well as the color and shape of the Set. Other names include: GraphDataSet, DataSet, GraphSet
    Since:
    <0.98.0
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Unknown
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
